---
title: Sesame-Crumbed Pork & Katsu Sauce with Jasmine Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: Katsu sauce is like the superhero sidekick of Japanese cuisine - bold, flavourful, and ready to take your tastebuds on an adventure!
Pour it over a golden crumbed pork dotted with sesame seeds, and watch as every bite become a delicious thrill ride.

